{"comments":"Animation Types — Canonical type definitions for animation system.\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis module defines the canonical types for the Hydrogen animation system.\nNEW CODE should import from here. Legacy modules (Animation.Algebra,\nGPU.DrawCommand, Typography.TextAnimation) have their own definitions\nthat will be migrated incrementally.\n\n## Type Categories\n\n1. **Easing**: Time-warping functions (Progress → Progress)\n2. **Stagger**: Spatial-to-temporal mapping for groups\n3. **Spring**: Physics-based animation state\n4. **Phase**: Normalized animation progress [0.0, 1.0]\n\n## Wire Format vs High-Level\n\nSome types have two forms:\n- **High-level**: Full expressiveness for composition (e.g., Easing with Custom)\n- **Wire-format**: Serializable subset for GPU dispatch (e.g., EasingId)\n\nConversion functions bridge these representations.\n\n## Migration Status\n\n- Animation.Algebra: Has own Easing, StaggerPattern, StaggerDirection\n- GPU.DrawCommand: Has EasingFunction, StaggerDirection for wire format\n- Typography.TextAnimation: Has StaggerDirection, StaggerPattern\n\nThese will be unified by:\n1. Adding re-exports from this module\n2. Updating Binary.purs to use conversion functions\n3. Deprecating duplicate definitions\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[140,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[140,3]},"title":"Linear"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[141,3]},"title":"EaseIn"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[142,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[142,3]},"title":"EaseOut"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[143,3]},"title":"EaseInOut"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[144,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[144,3]},"title":"EaseInQuad"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[145,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[145,3]},"title":"EaseOutQuad"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[146,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[146,3]},"title":"EaseInOutQuad"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[147,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[147,3]},"title":"EaseInCubic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[148,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[148,3]},"title":"EaseOutCubic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[149,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[149,3]},"title":"EaseInOutCubic"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[150,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[150,3]},"title":"EaseInQuart"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[151,3]},"title":"EaseOutQuart"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[152,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.purs","start":[152,3]},"title":"EaseInOutQuart"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Animation/Types.pur